fields.name: Coffee & Donut Doggy Bag
fields.description: Our beautiful coffe & donut doggy bag Features a rubber opening for the poo bags to pull through, zipper to refill your poo bag holder plus a handy clip to attach to your matching lead or waist belt. Made to be easy to clean and heavy duty for rough adventures, Doubles up as a handy carry pouch for treats or other small items. Free roll of poo bags included. Measures 8x5x5cm. Matching harness, collar, lead and bandana available

fields.name: Orange Rope Lead
fields.description: Our stylish orange rope lead will brighten up anyones day. Made with 100% cotton for that confort feeling. The lead is approximately 5ft in length and comes with a O ring in the handle to attach one of our doggy bags, your dog treats or to the other end of the leash to wear whilst out on your adventures. We recommend hand washing with mild soap and cold water.
